# System Sync Planning Checklist

When adding new POST endpoints, changing status transitions, modifying cache invalidation, or implementing user actions that trigger multi-system updates, verify all sync actions are covered.

**Full checklist:** [docs/SYSTEM_SYNC_ACTIONS_CHECKLIST.md](docs/SYSTEM_SYNC_ACTIONS_CHECKLIST.md)

## Quick Verification

1. **Webhooks:** Primary entity + Fileauditinglog (if applicable) + POSTLOG + adduser (if user) + notification (if notify)
2. **Cache:** Invalidate primary + related tables after every POST
3. **Status:** Use `statusStateMachine.validateTransition()` for status changes
4. **Frontend:** Refetch list/detail views after mutations
5. **Errors:** User feedback, retries (3x exponential backoff), no silent failures

