- `backend/API_ENDPOINTS_WEBHOOK_MAPPING.md` – webhook mapping
- `backend/src/services/statusTracking/statusStateMachine.ts` – transitions
- `backend/src/services/airtable/n8nClient.ts` – POST methods + cache invalidation
